Build ubuntu-jammy sdcard for Radxa rockpi4b:

Input files: ../uboot/out/idbloader.img
             ../uboot/out/uboot.img
             ../uboot/out/trust.img
             ../linux/out/boot.img
             ../rootfs-ubuntu-jammy/linaro-rootfs.img

./mksdcardimg.sh

The result is in sdcard.img

Plugin NVME SSD to PC.
sudo dd if=./sdcard.img of=/dev/sda bs=4096 conv=notrunc,fsync
Eject NVME SSD from PC, plugin NVME SSD to PC again.
sudo vi /media/$USER/rootfs/etc/gdm3/custom.conf ( uncomment WaylandEnable=false )
sync
sudo umount /media/$USER/rootfs
Eject NVME SSD from PC.

Plugin sdcard and NVME SSD to SBC
Login:
Username: linaro
Password: linaro
uname -a
lsb_release -a
sudo ifconfig
sudo vi /etc/apt/sources.list ( replace with http://mirrors.ocf.berkeley.edu/ubuntu-ports )
sudo dpkg-reconfigure tzdata
sudo dpkg-reconfigure locales
sync
sudo reboot

ps aux | grep -i apt ( wait till all apt done except grep -i apt )
sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade
sudo apt dist-upgrade
sudo vi /etc/systemd/logind.conf ( change to follows:
HandlePowerKey=ignore
HandleSuspendKey=ignore
HandleHibernateKey=ignore
HandleLidSwitch=ignore

sync
sudo shutdown -h now
Power off, power on
ps aux | grep -i apt ( wait till all apt done except grep -i apt )
glxinfo | grep OpenGL
date

sudo apt install speedtest-cli libjpeg-dev libpng-dev libpng16-16 pkg-config libx11-dev python3-pip python3-setuptools ffmpeg mpv glmark2 pandoc

speedtest-cli

glmark2

firefox -> youtube.com -> search YmDNhi07_Ho

git clone https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp.git
cd yt-dlp
make
cd ../
~/yt-dlp/yt-dlp -f 'bestvideo[ext=mp4]+bestaudio[ext=m4a]' hyUhEjtlDLA -o avemaria.mp4
mpv avemaria.mp4

sudo rfkill list
sudo rfkill unblock bluetooth
hciconfig hci0
hcitool dev
hciconfig -a
